Definition: the initial use of nuclear weapons to attack a country that also has nuclear weapons
Example: considered feasible only when the attacker can destroy the other country's ability to retaliate; the Pakistani president promised no first strike against India
Synonyms: strike, the, initial, use, of, nuclear, weapons, to, attack, a, country, that, also, has, considered, feasible, only, when, attacker, can, destroy, other, s, ability, retaliate, Pakistani, president, promised, no, first, against, India
Category: noun.act
